<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id7a03b254-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2006—<ref href="/us/pl/109/363">Pub. L. 109–363</ref> substituted “2 years after <date date="2006-10-17">October 17, 2006</date>,” for “<date date="2002-10-01">October 1, 2002</date>,”.</p>
</note>
